<Layout title="Booking Policy | Dolphin House Beach Resort">

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-44l font-extrabold text-center text-gray-800 mb-8">
      Booking & Cancellation Policy
    </h1>

    <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      We want every guest to enjoy a smooth and transparent booking experience at <strong>Dolphin House Beach Resort</strong>.
      Please read the following policies carefully before confirming your stay.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">1. Reservation Policy</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>All bookings are confirmed only after receipt of advance payment.</li>
          <li>Guests can make reservations directly through our website, WhatsApp, or phone.</li>
          <li>Rates may vary on weekends, holidays, and during festive seasons.</li>
          <li>Room allocation is subject to availability at the time of check-in.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">2. Check-in & Check-out</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Check-in Time:</strong> 12:00 PM</li>
          <li><strong>Check-out Time:</strong> 10:00 AM</li>
          <li>Early check-in or late check-out is subject to room availability and may incur additional charges.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">3. Payment Terms</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Advance payment is required to confirm your booking.</li>
          <li>Balance payment should be made during check-in at the resort.</li>
          <li>We accept payments via UPI, Google Pay, or bank transfer.</li>
          <li>All prices are inclusive of applicable taxes unless stated otherwise.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">4. Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Cancellations made <strong>7 days or more</strong> before check-in are eligible for a full refund of the advance.</li>
          <li>Cancellations made <strong>3‚Äì6 days</strong> before check-in will incur a 50% charge of the advance amount.</li>
          <li>Cancellations made <strong>within 48 hours</strong> of check-in or ‚Äúno-shows‚Äù are non-refundable.</li>
          <li>Refunds will be processed within 7‚Äì10 working days after cancellation confirmation.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">5. Modification Policy</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Booking dates may be changed once (subject to room availability) if requested at least 5 days before check-in.</li>
          <li>Rate differences may apply depending on the new dates.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">6. Child Policy</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Children below 5 years stay complimentary without extra bed.</li>
          <li>Extra person (above 5 years) charges apply as per the room rate (‚Çπ700 per person per night).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">7. Pets & Smoking Policy</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Pets are not allowed within the resort premises.</li>
          <li>Smoking is prohibited inside rooms; designated smoking areas are available outside.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">8. Force Majeure</h2>
        <p>
          Dolphin House Beach Resort will not be liable for delays or cancellations caused by circumstances beyond our control, 
          such as natural calamities, government restrictions, or other unforeseen events.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-3">9. Contact Us</h2>
